title: My Media Files v6.5 : Music Video Image Manage [Android - APK]
description:
My Media Files

Watch the video, listen to music, view images and documents, manage files.

-- Music ---
- Built-in music player.
- Bookmark any album, artist and genre.
- For music available section: all song, artist, album, genre, ringtone, alarm, recorded audio.
- Set song as ringtone for a contact.
- Widgets.

--- Video and Images ---
- Built-in video player, image viewer (supports GIF);
- Create images from GIF animation.
- View GIF animation by frames.
- Viewer for DOC, HTML, all text files.
- To open a video, images and other files, you can select other pre-installed software.

--- Manage Files ---
- Move or copy to a folder..
- Rename, share, delete, add to favorite.
- Work with zip archives: create a zip file, unzip.
- Create your own videos and photos from your camera.
- Create audio recording.

--- Search ---
- Quick search text in text files.
- Advanced search in web.
- Search by type and file extension.

--- Features ---
- All are divided into categories: music, video, image, document, all files.
- Folder and favorite by category.
- Add to bookmark any folder.
- Custom layout (list/grid).
- Information about file.
- Filter and sorting.
- Easy navigation bar.
- Multi-selection.



Required Android O/S : 4.0+


Localization : English, Chine, Japan, France, German, Italian, Turkich, Espania, Portugal, Arabic, Russian, Poland.


Google Play Link:               
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livecodedev.mymedia
